Class MatchingFilesNotifierService

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.content.Context
      • android.content.ContextWrapper
        • android.app.Service
          • vstore.android_filebox.services.MatchingFilesNotifierService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2

    public class MatchingFilesNotifierService
extends android.app.Service
    If new context is received, this service fetches files that match this context and notifies the user if new files are available.
